response.Q0: I clicked all of the fourth steps. I then chose the fourth step with the highest score to then click all three final steps coming out of that fourth step. Then I would take the route to the highest value. If all values of the three last steps were low, I would take the second-best fourth step and repeat. I also always clicked all three first steps as they always gave a positive bonus.
response.Q1: Yes, I learned that the first steps always gave a positive bonus. After I learned that, I always clicked the three first steps in each round.
